nhc_headline: ...HUMBERTO CONTINUES TO STRENGTHEN OVER THE CENTRAL ATLANTIC... ...EXPECTED TO BECOME A HURRICANE TOMORROW...
summary: ...HUMBERTO CONTINUES TO STRENGTHEN OVER THE CENTRAL ATLANTIC... ...EXPECTED TO BECOME A HURRICANE TOMORROW... As of 11:00 PM AST Thu Sep 25 the center of Humberto was located near 22.2, -57.1 with movement NW at 3 mph. The minimum central pressure was 998 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
